The directory bin and templates contain queuing scripts for recursive automatic submission.

Copy the bin directory into your home directory, along with the two templates corresponding to the system, and link CONFIG.default to the template file.

Requirements: grep, head, ls, sed, sort, awk.

(You may have to change some grep commands to the one in your system accepting extended regular expressions.)

---

For the nonblocking communication mode in JSC you need to add

export PYTHONPATH=/usr/local/rubik/rubik-1.0.1/.

to the file .profile
